      <title>菲律宾央行行长表示，菲律宾与中国的紧张局势打击了比索</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/philippines-china-tensions-hitting-peso-central-bank-chief-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[东南亚国家央行行长表示，菲律宾和中国之间因海洋主权争议而产生的紧张关系加剧了比索的压力，比索已跌至七个月低点，“升级将是投资者的一大担忧”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/philippines-china-tensions-hitting-peso-central-bank-chief-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 04:23:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马克龙推动武装欧洲变得更加紧迫——以及更危险的</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/emmanuel-macron-s-push-to-arm-europe-grows-more-urgent-and-more-dangerous</link>
      <description><![CDATA[马克龙一直在警告欧洲人的充满敌意的新世界正在迅速出现，但法国总统仍在努力说服合作伙伴相信他的判断。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/emmanuel-macron-s-push-to-arm-europe-grows-more-urgent-and-more-dangerous</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 04:00:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
